                </p>

                <p>
                    <span id="said_no_02895" class="said" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Lucy Steele" data-placement="auto top">"I am, &amp;c."</span>
                </p>

                <p>
                    <span id="said_no_02896" class="said" data-toggle="tooltip" title="aus.004.nar" data-placement="auto top">As soon as Elinor had
                        finished it, she performed what she concluded to be its writer's real
                        design, by placing it in the hands of Mrs. Jennings, who read it aloud with
